channel.description: We believe that interviewing is an art, and we practice it as such. Our courteous approach combined with a unique set of questions makes for candid interviews. Our content is carefully crafted, which is why Montreality interviews are held in high regard by Hip-Hop fans worldwide. We've conceived an interview format which inspires artists to let their guards down and simply have fun. It's safe to say that our YouTube channel is well on the way of becoming a Hip-Hop treasury. The goal is simple - scoring smiles :) !
